---
import problemImg from '@/assets/images/82c8c6459d7d.png';
---

<section class="section lhr-s3-problem">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="lhr-s3__layout">

      <div class="lhr-s3__content">

        <h2 class="lhr-s3__heading">The Struggle with Unwanted Hair</h2>

        <p class="lhr-s3__body">Dealing with unwanted hair is a constant battle. Traditional hair removal methods only offer temporary relief while creating ongoing problems:</p>

        <ul class="lhr-s3__list">
          <li>Daily shaving leaves skin irritated and stubble returns within days</li>
          <li>Painful waxing sessions for bikini areas and sensitive zones require regular maintenance</li>
          <li>Ingrown hairs and skin tone irregularities develop from repeated treatments</li>
          <li>At-home laser devices rarely deliver the permanent hair reduction results they promise</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="lhr-s3__body">Meanwhile, hair growth continues relentlessly, creating a frustrating cycle of time spent on temporary fixes that never deliver the smooth, lasting results you deserve.</p>

      </div>

      <div class="lhr-s3__img-col">
        <img
          src={problemImg.src}
          alt="Woman frustrated with traditional hair removal methods"
          class="lhr-s3__img"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          width="415"
          height="415"
        />
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .lhr-s3__layout {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .lhr-s3__content {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .lhr-s3__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .lhr-s3__body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .lhr-s3__list {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding-left: var(--space-md);
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .lhr-s3__img-col {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 415px;
  }

  .lhr-s3__img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .lhr-s3__img-col {
      width: 320px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .lhr-s3__layout {
      flex-direction: column-reverse;
    }

    .lhr-s3__img-col {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 415px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
</style>
